    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in fair condition, ideal for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a reasonable price. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though there is some minor fluid seepage under the engine and the suspension is beginning to show its age over bumps. The exterior has a few noticeable scratches and minor door dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery but remains clean and comfortable. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that performs well for its age but will eventually benefit from some routine maintenance and cosmetic attention.",
      "price": 20000.0,
